{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]}}}